.RE
.SH "KNOWN ISSUES AND BUGS"
.PP
\fBups\&.delay\&.shutdown is not honored\fR
.RS 4
Although that delay is properly set when sending the shutdown command, it seems some UPS ignore it and use a fixed 2 seconds delay instead\&.
.RE
